{"tid":1515893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除左winter on fire 仲可以考慮播逆權公民","createTime":"2019-08-29T10:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T11:08:14.000Z","uid":59818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bb8d30c3ea6760aa0cabc5250645c5e28bfad6b4","tid":1515893,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:52:48.000Z","msg":"逆權公民入面嘅六月民主運動同香港依家都好相似<br />\n又係六月 又係爭取普選 又有黑警 示威者都係比人唱係外國勢力<br />\n<br />\n電影入面冇一個主角 因為個個都係主角<br />\n教宗和尚 大學生 記者 良心警察 本來政治冷感嘅韓妹 勇武等等每一個都缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n而且電影易入口啲 最後ending感動得黎都幾令人有希望 冇winter on fire咁沉重<br />\n<br />\n最後就係可以係國際文宣上connect埋韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFVWvj3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFVWvj3.jpg&h=cb150e40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5e0e3d3bee1e99965c204ac7e03abf077ec5a2","tid":1515893,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc66cceb3423a39c7bf3a9372fe9cf0d146f9769","tid":1515893,"uid":269319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:57:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6218c1df6662676fb46991e545646a90f2c21dbe","tid":1515893,"uid":13149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"仲有逆權司機"},{"pid":"b62a249482e3e98e9cff9b34c8091ce696439e62","tid":1515893,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:01:39.000Z","msg":"逆權系列三套裝！"},{"pid":"b4a0872daf128ff5f56630ad4be24135251f7b1f","tid":1515893,"uid":65429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:02:14.000Z","msg":"播逆權司機同華麗的假期仲正<br />\n呢兩套又緊張又刺激"},{"pid":"e4e859f75d401cf4e6aeb75eefd583fc822e565c","tid":1515893,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit